The paper proposes a novel approach for automatic architecture search in deep learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV). The experiments conducted in the paper are focused on language modeling tasks, which further supports the likelihood of the paper belonging to the aforementioned sub-categories.
